<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Blog Page üìù</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(120deg, #ffecd2, #fcb69f);
      color: #333;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      min-height: 100vh;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 1000px;
      width: 100%;
      text-align: center;
      animation: fadeIn 1.5s ease;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 3em;
      color: #fff;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      text-shadow: 0 3px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    }

    p {
      font-size: 1.2em;
      color: #fffdfd;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    .posts {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
      gap: 25px;
    }

    .post {
      background: #fff;
      padding: 25px;
      border-radius: 15px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
      text-align: left;
      transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    }

    .post:hover {
      transform: translateY(-8px);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
    }

    .post h2 {
      font-size: 1.5em;
      color: #ff6f61;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .post p {
      color: #555;
      font-size: 1em;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    a.btn {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 40px;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: white;
      padding: 12px 28px;
      border-radius: 30px;
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 1.1em;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6f61, #ff9a9e);
      box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(255, 111, 97, 0.4);
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

    a.btn:hover {
      transform: scale(1.05);
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e94e3c, #ff758c);
    }

    @keyframes fadeIn {
      from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(30px);
      }
      to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Our Blog üìù</h1>
    <p>Latest thoughts, tips, and updates from our team üí°</p>

    <div class="posts">
      <div class="post">
        <h2>üå± Why We Love Fresh Fruits & Veggies</h2>
        <p>Eating fresh is not only healthy but also supports local farmers and the environment. We explore the benefits of going green and how you can start today!</p>
      </div>

      <div class="post">
        <h2>üöÄ Building with Express.js</h2>
        <p>Express makes backend development smooth and fun. Learn how we structure our apps and keep things simple using EJS and clean routing.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <a href="/product" class="btn">üõí Explore Our Products</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
